## âœ… Recommendations

1. **Launch weekend membership discounts** to attract casual riders who ride most on Saturdays and Sundays.
2. **Target commute-based promotions** to casual users who live in downtown areas.
3. **Use email/social campaigns** to highlight savings and convenience of annual plans.

